title: Lewica Events 2014-2015

@opening_2014
new-page: true
on-arrival: opening_2014_seen = 1

= January 2014: The Old Arrangement

The year opens with the familiar map still intact: Donald Tusk leads the PO-PSL government, Jaroslaw Kaczynski leads the main opposition, and Leszek Miller keeps the SLD in the Sejm as an aging but still organized third force.

The party can treat 2014 as another survival year, or start moving before the ground shifts under it.

- @opening_hold_third_force: Hold the line as a disciplined third force.
- @opening_early_renewal: Start renewal before the crisis forces it.
- @opening_issue_campaign: Prepare an issue campaign against both PO and PiS.

@opening_hold_third_force
on-arrival: {!
Q.resources = Math.min(10, Q.resources + 1);
Q.party_resources = Q.resources;
Q.sld_apparatus_strength = Math.min(10, Q.sld_apparatus_strength + 0.3);
Q.sld_apparatus_tension = Math.max(0, Q.sld_apparatus_tension - 2);
Q.sld_modernizers_dissent = Math.min(10, Q.sld_modernizers_dissent + 0.3);
!}

Miller keeps the machine calm. It is not inspiring, but discipline buys time and money.

- @post_event: Continue.

@opening_early_renewal
on-arrival: {!
Q.left_brand_strength = Math.min(10, Q.left_brand_strength + 0.4);
Q.sld_modernizers_strength = Math.min(10, Q.sld_modernizers_strength + 0.5);
Q.under_30_left += 0.7 * Q.party_efficiency;
Q.unaffiliated_left += 0.5 * Q.party_efficiency;
Q.sld_apparatus_dissent = Math.min(10, Q.sld_apparatus_dissent + 0.4);
Q.gawkowski_network_strength = Math.min(10, Q.gawkowski_network_strength + 0.2);
!}

The modernizers get room before they can be dismissed as panic after defeat.

- @post_event: Continue.

@opening_issue_campaign
on-arrival: {!
Q.left_brand_strength = Math.min(10, Q.left_brand_strength + 0.3);
Q.urban_working_class_left += 0.8 * Q.party_efficiency;
Q.unaffiliated_left += 0.4 * Q.party_efficiency;
Q.ko_relation = Math.max(-10, Q.ko_relation - 1);
Q.pis_relation = Math.max(-10, Q.pis_relation - 1);
Q.pps_up_strength = Math.min(10, Q.pps_up_strength + 0.3);
!}

The SLD tries to make the year about wages, pensions, secularism, and public services before the PO-PiS duel absorbs the air.

- @post_event: Continue.

@maidan_2014
new-page: true
on-arrival: {!
Q.maidan_2014_seen = 1;
Q.russian_threat_level = Math.max(Q.russian_threat_level, 5);
!}

= February 2014: Maidan Reaches Warsaw

The Euromaidan crisis stops being a foreign-news item. Radoslaw Sikorski is active in Kyiv, the government speaks the language of state responsibility, and every Polish party has to decide whether Ukraine is central to its message.

- @maidan_state_line: Back the pro-Ukraine state line.
- @maidan_domestic_focus: Keep the SLD focused on domestic economics.
- @maidan_left_solidarity: Frame Ukraine as democratic and social solidarity.

@maidan_state_line
on-arrival: {!
Q.ukrainian_alignment = Math.min(10, Q.ukrainian_alignment + 0.8);
Q.eu_institutional_alignment = Math.min(10, Q.eu_institutional_alignment + 0.2);
Q.ko_relation += 1;
Q.media_reach = Math.min(10, Q.media_reach + 0.2);
Q.tr_residue_dissent = Math.min(10, Q.tr_residue_dissent + 0.2);
!}

The party sounds responsible and pro-Western, but it risks disappearing into the government's line.

- @post_event: Continue.

@maidan_domestic_focus
on-arrival: {!
Q.resources = Math.min(10, Q.resources + 1);
Q.party_resources = Q.resources;
Q.ukrainian_alignment = Math.max(0, Q.ukrainian_alignment - 0.2);
Q.urban_working_class_left += 0.5 * Q.party_efficiency;
Q.pps_up_dissent = Math.max(0, Q.pps_up_dissent - 0.2);
!}

The SLD keeps talking about living standards. It avoids a policy trap, but looks smaller during a regional crisis.

- @post_event: Continue.

@maidan_left_solidarity
on-arrival: {!
Q.ukrainian_alignment = Math.min(10, Q.ukrainian_alignment + 0.5);
Q.civil_society_capital = Math.min(10, Q.civil_society_capital + 0.4);
Q.unaffiliated_left += 0.5 * Q.party_efficiency;
Q.under_30_left += 0.5 * Q.party_efficiency;
Q.sld_apparatus_dissent = Math.min(10, Q.sld_apparatus_dissent + 0.2);
!}

The party avoids both Kremlin nostalgia and empty Atlanticism, using the crisis to speak about democratic self-organization.

- @post_event: Continue.

@crimea_2014
