!}

= June 2014: The Tape Affair

The Wprost recordings tear through the governing camp. The Belka-Sienkiewicz conversation and the later ABW entry into the newsroom turn a scandal into a question about institutions, elites, and the state.

- @tape_attack_elites: Attack PO as a self-protecting elite.
- @tape_institutional_cleanup: Demand institutional cleanup and media freedom.
- @tape_left_economics: Use the scandal to pivot back to economic insecurity.

@tape_attack_elites
on-arrival: {!
Q.ko_relation = Math.max(-10, Q.ko_relation - 4);
Q.urban_working_class_ko -= 0.8;
Q.unaffiliated_ko -= 0.8;
Q.unaffiliated_left += 0.6 * Q.party_efficiency;
Q.populist_realignment_pressure = Math.min(10, Q.populist_realignment_pressure + 0.3);
Q.left_brand_strength = Math.min(10, Q.left_brand_strength + 0.2);
!}

The attack lands, but it also feeds the broader anti-elite wave that PiS and Kukiz-style politics can use more easily.

- @post_event: Continue.

@tape_institutional_cleanup
on-arrival: {!
Q.ko_relation = Math.max(-10, Q.ko_relation - 1);
Q.constitutional_crisis_risk = Math.max(0, Q.constitutional_crisis_risk - 0.1);
Q.civil_society_capital = Math.min(10, Q.civil_society_capital + 0.3);
Q.urban_professionals_left += 0.6 * Q.party_efficiency;
Q.media_reach = Math.min(10, Q.media_reach + 0.2);
!}

The party criticizes the government without copying anti-state rhetoric.

- @post_event: Continue.

@tape_left_economics
on-arrival: {!
Q.urban_working_class_left += 0.9 * Q.party_efficiency;
Q.age_50_65_left += 0.5 * Q.party_efficiency;
Q.pps_up_strength = Math.min(10, Q.pps_up_strength + 0.2);
Q.media_reach = Math.max(0, Q.media_reach - 0.1);
Q.ko_relation = Math.max(-10, Q.ko_relation - 2);
!}

The SLD argues that restaurant cynicism matters because ordinary voters are still dealing with jobs, pensions, and services.

- @post_event: Continue.

@tape_aftershock_2014
new-page: true
on-arrival: tape_aftershock_2014_seen = 1

= July 2014: Tusk Survives

The government wins its confidence vote, PiS cannot convert the tape affair into a change of cabinet, and the scandal becomes a slow poison rather than an immediate collapse.

- @aftershock_keep_pressure: Keep pressure on PO.
- @aftershock_move_on: Move back to local and social campaigning.
- @aftershock_anti_corruption: Build an anti-corruption reform package.

@aftershock_keep_pressure
on-arrival: {!
Q.ko_relation = Math.max(-10, Q.ko_relation - 2);
Q.left_campaign_bonus += 0.2 * Q.party_efficiency;
Q.populist_realignment_pressure = Math.min(10, Q.populist_realignment_pressure + 0.2);
Q.pis_kaczynski_strength = Math.min(10, Q.pis_kaczynski_strength + 0.2);
!}

The scandal remains useful, though the sharper anti-system energy does not naturally belong to the SLD.

- @post_event: Continue.

@aftershock_move_on
on-arrival: {!
Q.left_regional_rebuild += 0.5;
Q.left_campaign_bonus += 0.15 * Q.party_efficiency;
Q.urban_working_class_left += 0.5 * Q.party_efficiency;
Q.sld_apparatus_dissent = Math.max(0, Q.sld_apparatus_dissent - 0.2);
!}

The party decides that November's local election will matter more than another week of outrage.

- @post_event: Continue.

@aftershock_anti_corruption
on-arrival: {!
Q.civil_society_capital = Math.min(10, Q.civil_society_capital + 0.3);
Q.left_brand_strength = Math.min(10, Q.left_brand_strength + 0.3);
Q.urban_professionals_left += 0.5 * Q.party_efficiency;
Q.media_reach = Math.min(10, Q.media_reach + 0.2);
Q.resources = Math.max(0, Q.resources - 1);
Q.party_resources = Q.resources;
!}

It costs time and staff, but the SLD gets a cleaner institutional argument.

- @post_event: Continue.

@tusk_eu_2014
new-page: true
on-arrival: {!
Q.tusk_eu_2014_seen = 1;
Q.ko_tusk_strength = Math.max(0, Q.ko_tusk_strength - 0.7);
Q.eu_institutional_alignment = Math.min(10, Q.eu_institutional_alignment + 0.4);
!}

= August 2014: Tusk Goes To Europe

Donald Tusk is chosen to lead the European Council. It is a major Polish success in Brussels and, at the same time, a succession shock for Platforma.

- @tusk_respect_success: Respect the state success.
- @tusk_escape_line: Say Tusk is escaping domestic accountability.
- @tusk_left_opening: Treat the succession as an opening for the left.

@tusk_respect_success
on-arrival: {!
Q.eu_institutional_alignment = Math.min(10, Q.eu_institutional_alignment + 0.3);
Q.ko_relation += 1;
Q.urban_professionals_left += 0.3 * Q.party_efficiency;
Q.media_reach = Math.min(10, Q.media_reach + 0.1);
!}

The SLD sounds statesmanlike, but it gives PO some of the prestige frame.

- @post_event: Continue.

@tusk_escape_line
on-arrival: {!
Q.ko_relation = Math.max(-10, Q.ko_relation - 3);
Q.unaffiliated_left += 0.5 * Q.party_efficiency;
Q.populist_realignment_pressure = Math.min(10, Q.populist_realignment_pressure + 0.2);
Q.pis_kaczynski_strength = Math.min(10, Q.pis_kaczynski_strength + 0.1);
!}

The line is simple and media-friendly, but PiS can shout it louder.

- @post_event: Continue.

@tusk_left_opening
on-arrival: {!
Q.left_brand_strength = Math.min(10, Q.left_brand_strength + 0.3);
Q.sld_modernizers_strength = Math.min(10, Q.sld_modernizers_strength + 0.3);
Q.urban_professionals_left += 0.5 * Q.party_efficiency;
Q.urban_working_class_left += 0.4 * Q.party_efficiency;
Q.ko_tusk_strength = Math.max(0, Q.ko_tusk_strength - 0.2);
!}

The party argues that without Tusk's personal dominance, the old PO-PiS rhythm can be broken.

- @post_event: Continue.

@kopacz_government_2014
new-page: true
on-arrival: {!
Q.kopacz_government_2014_seen = 1;
Q.prime_minister = "Ewa Kopacz";
Q.ko_tusk_strength = Math.max(0, Q.ko_tusk_strength - 0.5);
Q.ko_schetyna_residual_strength = Math.min(10, Q.ko_schetyna_residual_strength + 0.3);
!}

= September 2014: The Kopacz Government

Ewa Kopacz takes over the PO-PSL government. The coalition is still in office, but the central figure who held Platforma together is no longer prime minister.

- @kopacz_test_government: Test the new government immediately.
- @kopacz_working_channel: Keep parliamentary channels open.
- @kopacz_women_leadership: Use the transition to speak to women voters.

@kopacz_test_government
on-arrival: {!
Q.ko_relation = Math.max(-10, Q.ko_relation - 2);
Q.left_campaign_bonus += 0.2 * Q.party_efficiency;
Q.media_reach = Math.min(10, Q.media_reach + 0.2);
Q.urban_working_class_ko -= 0.5;
!}

The SLD treats Kopacz as a premier who has to earn authority, not inherit it.

- @post_event: Continue.

@kopacz_working_channel
on-arrival: {!
Q.ko_relation += 2;
Q.sld_apparatus_dissent = Math.max(0, Q.sld_apparatus_dissent - 0.2);
Q.tr_residue_dissent = Math.min(10, Q.tr_residue_dissent + 0.2);
Q.urban_professionals_left += 0.3 * Q.party_efficiency;
!}

The party keeps anti-PiS parliamentary options alive, even if it blurs opposition lines.

- @post_event: Continue.

@kopacz_women_leadership
on-arrival: {!
Q.women_under_50_left += 0.8 * Q.party_efficiency;
Q.women_over_50_left += 0.5 * Q.party_efficiency;
Q.civil_society_capital = Math.min(10, Q.civil_society_capital + 0.2);
Q.sld_modernizers_strength = Math.min(10, Q.sld_modernizers_strength + 0.2);
Q.sld_apparatus_dissent = Math.min(10, Q.sld_apparatus_dissent + 0.2);
!}

The SLD does not attack Kopacz personally; it pivots to childcare, work, health care, and reproductive autonomy.

- @post_event: Continue.

@sikorski_politico_2014
new-page: true
on-arrival: sikorski_politico_2014_seen = 1

= October 2014: Sikorski's Foreign-Policy Mess

Radoslaw Sikorski's Politico remarks about Putin, Tusk, and Ukraine produce a communications crisis just as the new governing arrangement is trying to look steady.

- @sikorski_state_credibility: Call for disciplined foreign policy.
- @sikorski_attack_chaos: Attack PO's chaos.
- @sikorski_avoid_trap: Avoid the story and keep local focus.

@sikorski_state_credibility
on-arrival: {!
Q.ukrainian_alignment = Math.min(10, Q.ukrainian_alignment + 0.2);
Q.eu_institutional_alignment = Math.min(10, Q.eu_institutional_alignment + 0.2);
Q.left_brand_strength = Math.min(10, Q.left_brand_strength + 0.2);
Q.urban_professionals_left += 0.4 * Q.party_efficiency;
!}

The SLD looks serious without pretending the gaffe is the only thing in politics.

- @post_event: Continue.

@sikorski_attack_chaos
on-arrival: {!
Q.ko_relation = Math.max(-10, Q.ko_relation - 2);
Q.media_reach = Math.min(10, Q.media_reach + 0.2);
Q.unaffiliated_left += 0.4 * Q.party_efficiency;
Q.pis_kaczynski_strength = Math.min(10, Q.pis_kaczynski_strength + 0.1);
!}

The attack hurts PO, but the main beneficiary of a security-chaos story may still be PiS.

- @post_event: Continue.

@sikorski_avoid_trap
on-arrival: {!
Q.left_regional_rebuild += 0.4;
Q.left_campaign_bonus += 0.15 * Q.party_efficiency;
Q.rural_west_left += 0.4 * Q.party_efficiency;
Q.sld_apparatus_strength = Math.min(10, Q.sld_apparatus_strength + 0.2);
!}

The party lets the foreign-policy elite argue while SLD county structures prepare for November.

- @post_event: Continue.

