Q.left_brand_strength = Math.max(0, Q.left_brand_strength - 0.2);
Q.sld_apparatus_dissent = Math.max(0, Q.sld_apparatus_dissent - 0.2);
Q.sld_modernizers_dissent = Math.min(10, Q.sld_modernizers_dissent + 0.8);
Q.tr_residue_dissent = Math.min(10, Q.tr_residue_dissent + 0.8);
Q.razem_external = 1;
!}

The safer threshold may save representation, but it signals that the old party has not solved the broader left's crisis.

- @post_event: Continue.

